   Laport, Robert G., Rhodes Coll, Dept Biol, Memphis, TN 38112 USA.
   Minckley, Robert L., Univ Rochester, Dept Biol, Rochester, NY 14627 USA.
   Pilson, Diana, Univ Nebraska Lincoln, Sch Biol Sci, Lincoln, NE 68588 USA.},
